description: Creates a usage plan key for adding an existing API key to a usage plan.

parameters.name: usagePlanId
parameters.description: The Id of the UsagePlan resource representing the usage plan containing the to-be-created UsagePlanKey resource representing a plan customer.

parameters.name: keyId
parameters.description: The identifier of a UsagePlanKey resource for a plan customer.

parameters.name: keyType
parameters.description: The type of a UsagePlanKey resource for a plan customer.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The Id of a usage plan key.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The type of a usage plan key. Currently, the valid key type is API_KEY.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The value of a usage plan key.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of a usage plan key.
